fulltitle: Maj. John Newman: Afghanistan and Vietnam
title: Maj. John Newman: Afghanistan and Vietnam
description:
JANUARY 4, 2010 | Major John Newman talked about President Kennedy’s handling of Vietnam and compared his policy toward Vietnam with President Obama’s Afghanistan policy. He also responded to telephone calls and electronic communications.

John Newman is the author of JKF and Vietnam: Deception, Intrigue, and the Struggle for Power (Warner Books; February 1992).
